entries.journal_entry_description: The creatures in the Atrium, on the top floor of the Tansarii Point Station, have run amok and are destroying Car'das property. You should investigate.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Use the elevator to go to the Atrium.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Atrium
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Destroy 5 flits in the Atrium before they cause any more damage.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Kill the Flits in the Atrium
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Destroy 5 Scyks in the Atrium before they cause any more damage.
entries.task02_journal_entry_title: Kill the Scyks in the Atrium
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Now that you have killed the menacing creatures, use the elevator to return to the main level.
entries.task03_journal_entry_title: Use the Elevator to go to the Main Level
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Now that you have killed the creatures in the Atrium, return to Rydel.
entries.task04_journal_entry_title: Return to Rydel Delan in the Close Combat Training Center
